    "tiktok-music": {
      "title": "Tiktok Music",
      "role": [
        "Brand strategy",
        "Artist & label partnerships",
        "Creative production",
        "Content strategy"
      ],
      "slides": [
        {
          "image": "media/2d60896c83ac9f8d920d33007ab886f1.jpeg",
          "richText": [
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "64a0ee00d0b3",
              "style": "normal",
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "40189d969267",
                  "text": "Music is the lifeblood of TikTok. From artists who go from bedroom stars to international pop stars, to users who dance, do makeup trends, and create memes based on Sounds and songs, it is the driving force of the platform.",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "image": "media/TTM_Music Hub Banners_0420_002_Banner 1 - Search.avif",
          "richText": [
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "cd6854adc281",
              "style": "normal",
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "c527b9c29b97",
                  "text": "As a content strategy lead in music editorial, it was my job to evangelize the success stories on the platform and also expose music happenings to users on and off-platform of what's happening in silos they may not be part of.",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "image": "media/TTM_EOY Rompiendo Composite_9x16_1215_003.avif",
          "richText": [
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "009aa7231e0d",
              "style": "normal",
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "f8b5d5429bb1",
                  "text": "As a result, we developed @MusicOnTikTok, a standalone brand that evangelized the story of music on TikTok across new touchpoints.",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "image": "media/PENDRY_09_AD127_TIK7_JasonDerulo2_v01_CamRec_072021_1.mp4",
          "richText": [
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "0cca7230ac7a",
              "style": "normal",
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "769dfd574b53",
                  "text": "To launch that, we contracted an agency and began developing content series and features that would serve as a conduit for storytelling, as well as a permanent placement we could use as a relationship-builder with music talent, labels and managers.",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "image": "media/Screenshot 2026-03-30 at 1.45.05 PM.png",
          "title": "Results",
          "richText": [
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "4677a46c5aba",
              "style": "normal",
              "listItem": "bullet",
              "level": 1,
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "c01ebca9fdba",
                  "text": "397,100 organic followers on TikTok",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "9f79cf5985e9",
              "style": "normal",
              "listItem": "bullet",
              "level": 1,
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "76279e983572",
                  "text": "55,000 organic followers on Instagram",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "3e3c71e0706e",
              "style": "normal",
              "listItem": "bullet",
              "level": 1,
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "cba40e079f9f",
                  "text": "Became a revenue-driving platform that led to brand and music festival partnerships",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "b57f049a2df6",
              "style": "normal",
              "listItem": "bullet",
              "level": 1,
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "74ded704a9ff",
                  "text": "TikTok's own music festival, and several brand content series",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    "sonic": {
      "title": "Sonic",
      "role": [],
      "slides": [
        {
          "image": "media/SonicUnicornDreamsSlush.png",
          "title": "Optional Title",
          "richText": [
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "df03f68ae988",
              "style": "normal",
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "ca4e64468dda",
                  "text": "Sonic had a product so visually distinctive and culturally resonant it practically created its own demand. The challenge was turning that latent desire into a moment — one that would drive traffic, generate buzz, and make the limited-time offering feel like a true cultural event.",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "image": "",
          "title": "",
          "richText": [
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "73704772036d",
              "style": "normal",
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "e46502b9b635",
                  "text": "We built an integrated campaign around the Unicorn Dream Slush that leaned into the product's inherently shareable aesthetic, tapping into the cultural conversation around fantasy, escapism and color.",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "image": "media/SonicUnicornDreamsSlush2.png",
          "title": "",
          "richText": [
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "8648acc81352",
              "style": "normal",
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "5bccf21e9912",
                  "text": "The strategy connected platform-first social with influencer amplification and in-store activation — and the resulting story became the centerpiece of a broader case study: \"The Making of a Myth: How SONIC's Unicorn Horn Straw Became a Cultural Artifact.\"",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "image": "",
          "title": "Results",
          "richText": [
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "85988d9ab244",
              "style": "normal",
              "listItem": "bullet",
              "level": 1,
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "f0e4aa159037",
                  "text": "10% increase in same-store sales",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "2511d81c4f47",
              "style": "normal",
              "listItem": "bullet",
              "level": 1,
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "cecd7b47556a",
                  "text": "Sold out across the country",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "a4a73636d28c",
              "style": "normal",
              "listItem": "bullet",
              "level": 1,
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "04d8bf974894",
                  "text": "Created a secondary resale market on eBay that also sold out",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "7e9f0476537e",
              "style": "normal",
              "listItem": "bullet",
              "level": 1,
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "ca2aea4fb7a3",
                  "text": "PRWeek 2026 nominations: Best Consumer Launch and Best Content",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "b8dab069c712",
              "style": "normal",
              "listItem": "bullet",
              "level": 1,
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "a00c48712204",
                  "text": "Shorty Awards 2026 nominations: Storytelling and Restaurants categories",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "86a0be6c7d7c",
