    "chevrolet": {
      "title": "Chevrolet Bolt with Tiagz",
      "role": [
        "Brand partnerships",
        "Creator strategy",
        "Creator-client partnership lead",
        "Programming team liaison"
      ],
      "slides": [
        {
          "image": "media/2023-chevrolet-bolt_459v.1200.jpg.webp",
          "title": "",
          "richText": [
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "a83beb5dd127",
              "style": "normal",
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "f9a9d2c4579d",
                  "text": "One of the remits of TikTok's music team was to make artists who were popping on the platform pop off-platform — showing the efficacy of being a presence on TikTok as an artist.",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "image": "",
          "title": "The solution",
          "richText": [
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "fff97308e506",
              "style": "normal",
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "a35e3ee0ee8f",
                  "text": "One way to do that is to get the artists paid. In 2021, we worked with Chevrolet to develop a creator-led campaign that paired star creator Tiagz with the Chevrolet Bolt EUV in Canada — a campaign that broke new ground for what a brand-creator partnership on the platform could look like.",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "image": "",
          "title": "Results",
          "richText": [
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "d39cfddd40e6",
              "style": "normal",
              "listItem": "bullet",
              "level": 1,
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "f912ee1e1775",
                  "text": "First music branded effect on the platform",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "088029b3f754",
              "style": "normal",
              "listItem": "bullet",
              "level": 1,
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "317e8af599c6",
                  "text": "First auto brand to collaborate with a musician for a custom song",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "62e3412a5958",
              "style": "normal",
              "listItem": "bullet",
              "level": 1,
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "0e5b7c4c6f5a",
                  "text": "First auto brand to use Interactive Add-On",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            },
            {
